values:
Just once, I would like to find something I'm good at.&nbsp; Not great even, just good.&nbsp; And it would be oh so nice if I could actually manage to make a living (and no, not a grand one) at this something.&nbsp; 

I just lately seem to be pretty below par on everything.&nbsp; And working hard at it too!

Where is your guidance councilor when you need one?
